  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/d1346586b0ce9bb82c4d4a9320699ab4.avif?t=1695220888\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/d2b8fe3b169bbef192aaada96b417fac.poster.avif?t=1695220888\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/d2b8fe3b169bbef192aaada96b417fac.webm?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/d2b8fe3b169bbef192aaada96b417fac.mp4?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Scribbler is a scholar who cannot remember his past while Patch is a unique breed of dragon, a ´Chimeragon´, with new, unexpected powers they discover along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/bf9388f9b0c20f1b6ebe4db7dd4a41bd.avif?t=1695220888\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/2e2a871c9b3cc1ca960b3270a62e694f.poster.avif?t=1695220888\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/2e2a871c9b3cc1ca960b3270a62e694f.webm?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/2e2a871c9b3cc1ca960b3270a62e694f.mp4?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join the new heroic duo, Scribbler, and Patch, in an epic battle to save dragons and defeat the villain, Eir, who is controlling dragons to carry out her evil plans. Clash against fierce enemies, explore new and familiar locations, meet many favorite DreamWorks Dragons characters, and recover the memories that reveal Patch’s true origin in this fun and fiery action-adventure game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/40934a7312d4e86b1faadb7e4a34cf0e.avif?t=1695220888\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/270ef5032c3e1de3302a7bf84f28b15d.poster.avif?t=1695220888\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/270ef5032c3e1de3302a7bf84f28b15d.webm?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/270ef5032c3e1de3302a7bf84f28b15d.mp4?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A NEW ADVENTURE </strong>- Recover Scribbler’s lost memories as you forge a friendship with Patch, his ultimate hybrid dragon<br></li><li><strong>BATTLE</strong> - Unlock powerful abilities and take on fearsome foes<br></li><li><strong>EXPLORE</strong>  - Fly to new and familiar locations including Havenholme, Valka’s Mountain and Blood Briar Island <br></li><li><strong>SOLVE PUZZLES</strong> - Swap between Scribbler and his dragon Patch to conquer obstacles</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/d1346586b0ce9bb82c4d4a9320699ab4.avif?t=1695220888\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/d2b8fe3b169bbef192aaada96b417fac.poster.avif?t=1695220888\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/d2b8fe3b169bbef192aaada96b417fac.webm?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/d2b8fe3b169bbef192aaada96b417fac.mp4?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Scribbler is a scholar who cannot remember his past while Patch is a unique breed of dragon, a ´Chimeragon´, with new, unexpected powers they discover along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/bf9388f9b0c20f1b6ebe4db7dd4a41bd.avif?t=1695220888\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/2e2a871c9b3cc1ca960b3270a62e694f.poster.avif?t=1695220888\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/2e2a871c9b3cc1ca960b3270a62e694f.webm?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896960/extras/2e2a871c9b3cc1ca960b3270a62e694f.mp4?t=1695220888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join the new heroic duo, Scribbler, and Patch, in an epic battle to save dragons and defeat the villain,